Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: tiddlywebplugins.virtualhosting
Version: 0.1
Summary: Enable virtualhosts from the same tiddlyweb server.
Home-page: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/tiddlywebplugins.virtualhosting
Author: Chris Dent
Author-email: cdent@peermore.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: 
        This plugin overrides tiddlyweb.web.util:server_host_url
        to pay attention to the HTTP_HOST variable if it is present
        and use it for creating outgoing urls instead of the url
        provided by the server_host settings in config.
        
        Copyright 2010, Chris Dent <cdent@peermore.com>
        
        Licensed under the same terms as TiddlyWeb.
        
Platform: Posix; MacOS X; Windows
